public abstract class AbstractResource
extends Object
implements IResource

Convenience resource implementation. The subclass must implement newResourceResponse(org.apache.wicket.request.resource.IResource.Attributes) method.

flushResponseAfterHeaders

protected void flushResponseAfterHeaders(WebResponse response)
Flushes the response after setting the headers. This is necessary for Firefox if this resource is an image, otherwise it messes up other images on page.

Parameters:
response - the current web response
